<!-- ------------------------- START : Description ------------------------- -->
<p align="justify"><a href="https://quantized8.github.io/Test-Repo999"><strong><em>Test Repo999</em></strong></a> is a free and open-source toolkit <b>empowering the development of open-source Python projects on GitHub</b>. It is a <b>dynamic repository template</b> that provides a complete, professional, and robust infrastructure for your project, where the only thing missing is your code. With Test Repo999, you can solely focus on what truly matters: implementing your ideas and bringing your vision to life!</p>

<h2>Key Features</h2>
<picture><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Automation&color=135400&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Automation&color=459B24&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"><img title="Automation" alt="Automation" height="35px" src="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Automation&color=135400&label="></picture>
<p align="justify">Test Repo999 streamlines a remarkable portion of the process of creating, documenting, testing, publishing, and maintaining Python packages, making your project development a pleasant breeze!</p>
<picture><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Synchronization&color=135400&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Synchronization&color=459B24&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"><img title="Synchronization" alt="Synchronization" height="35px" src="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Synchronization&color=135400&label="></picture>
<p align="justify">Test Repo999 gathers all your project's key information and configuration in one place, and dynamically updates them throughout your repository, Python package, and documentation website.</p>
<picture><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Configuration&color=135400&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Configuration&color=459B24&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"><img title="Configuration" alt="Configuration" height="35px" src="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Configuration&color=135400&label="></picture>
<p align="justify">Test Repo999 elevates your project by providing full configuration for your repository, Python package, and documentation website, according to the latest guidelines and best practices.</p>
<picture><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Customization&color=135400&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Customization&color=459B24&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"><img title="Customization" alt="Customization" height="35px" src="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Customization&color=135400&label="></picture>
<p align="justify">While carefully configured, Test Repo999 is also fully customizable, allowing you to tailor every aspect of your development pipeline to your specific needs</p>
<picture><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Documentation&color=135400&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Documentation&color=459B24&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"><img title="Documentation" alt="Documentation" height="35px" src="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Documentation&color=135400&label="></picture>
<p align="justify">Test Repo999 comes with a professional website for your project, that is easily customizable, and automatically generated and deployed on your preferred platform.</p>
<picture><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Production&color=135400&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"><source srcset="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Production&color=459B24&label=" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"><img title="Production" alt="Production" height="35px" src="https://img.shields.io/static/v1?style=for-the-badge&message=Production&color=135400&label="></picture>
<p align="justify">With Test Repo999, the only remaining step to publishing a production-ready Python project is adding your code, unit-tests and documentation content.</p>
